cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY 

This paper focuses on learning to control robots directly based on images, which is a primary challenge in robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses reinforcement learning approaches, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper focuses on image-based control, which could place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses learning action policies, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses the transfer of policies to the real-world, which could place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control).
